<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/graduate-students-research-pushes-discoveries-toward-clinical-trials/">Graduate students’ research pushes discoveries toward clinical trials</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
